            <p>
              His private code states that etiquette outranks truth if it keeps the room calm. Staff refer to the
              handbook as “the velvet rulebook.”
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card-link">
            <h2>Proof of Virtue</h2>
            <p>
              Twice a year he attends St. Bartholomew’s, sitting in pew three. He donates to the flower guild the night
              before for maximum bulletin visibility.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card-link">
            <h2>Boardroom Persona</h2>
            <p>
              Monty keeps a decanter of “negotiation sherry” in every office he visits, insisting it smooths tempers and
              polishes reputations in equal measure.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
